#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:3
msgid "Telescope Setup"
msgstr "Configurar el telescopi"

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:5
msgid ""
"Most telescopes are equipped with RS232 interface for remote control. "
"Connect the RS232 jack in your telescope to your computer's Serial/USB port. "
"Traditionally, the RS232 connects to the serial port of your computer, but "
"since many new laptops abandoned the serial port in favor of USB/FireWire "
"ports, you might need to obtain a Serial to USB adaptor to use with new "
"laptops."
msgstr ""
"La majoria de telescopis estan equipats amb una interfĂ­cie RS232 per al "
"control remot. Connecteu el connector RS232 del telescopi amb el port sĂ¨rie/"
"USB de l'ordinador. Tradicionalment, l'RS232 es connecta al port sĂ¨rie de "
"l'ordinador, perĂ² com que molts ordinadors portĂ tils nous han abandonat el "
"port sĂ¨rie en favor dels ports USB/FireWire, Ă©s possible que necessiteu un "
"adaptador sĂ¨rie-USB per a utilitzar-lo amb els ordinadors portĂ tils nous."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:13
msgid ""
"After connecting your telescope to the Serial/USB port, turn your telescope "
"on. It is *highly* recommended that you download and install the latest "
"firmware for your telescope controller."
msgstr ""
"DesprĂ©s de connectar el telescopi amb el port sĂ¨rie o USB, inicieu-lo. Es "
"recomana *molt*, que baixeu i instalÂ·leu el microprogramari mĂ©s recent per "
"al controlador del telescopi."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:17
msgid ""
"The telescope needs to be aligned before it can be used properly. Align your "
"telescope (one or two stars alignment) as illustrated in your telescope "
"manual."
msgstr ""
"El telescopi necessita ser alineat abans de poder-lo utilitzar correctament. "
"Alineeu-lo (alineaciĂ³ d'una o dues estreles) tal com s'ilÂ·lustra al manual "
"del telescopi."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:21
msgid ""
"KStars needs to verify time and location settings before connecting to the "
"telescope. This insures proper tracking and synchronization between the "
"telescope and KStars. The following steps will enable you to connect to a "
"device that is connected to your computer. To connect and control remote "
"devices, please refer to :doc:`remote device control <indi-remote-control>` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"KStars necessita verificar la configuraciĂ³ del temps i emplaĂ§ament abans de "
"connectar-se amb el telescopi. AĂ§Ă² garantix un seguiment i una "
"sincronitzaciĂ³ adequats entre el telescopi i KStars. Els passos segĂ¼ents vos "
"permetran connectar-vos amb un dispositiu que estiga connectat amb "
"l'amfitriĂ³. Per a connectar i controlar els dispositius remots, referiu-vos "
"a la secciĂ³ :doc:`Control remot dels dispositius <indi-remote-control>`."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:29
msgid ""
"You can use the Telescope Setup Wizard and it will verify all the required "
"information in the process. It can automatically scan ports for attached "
"telescopes. You can run the wizard by selecting the ``Devices`` â†’ "
"``Telescope Wizard`` menu item."
msgstr ""
"Podeu utilitzar l'Assistent de configuraciĂ³ del telescopi i este verificarĂ  "
"tota la informaciĂ³ necessĂ ria durant el procĂ©s. Pot escanejar automĂ ticament "
"els ports dels telescopis connectats. Podeu executar l'assistent "
"seleccionant l'element de menĂº ``Dispositius`` â†’ ``Assistent del telescopiâ€¦"
"``."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:34
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can connect to a local telescope by performing the "
"following steps:"
msgstr ""
"De manera alternativa, podeu connectar amb un telescopi local seguint els "
"passos segĂ¼ents:"

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:37
msgid ""
"Set your geographical location. Open the ``Set Geographic Location`` window "
"by selecting the ``Settings`` â†’ ``Geographic...`` menu item, or by pressing "
"the ``Globe`` icon in the toolbar, or by pressing **Ctrl**\\ +\\ **G**."
msgstr ""
"Establiu el vostre emplaĂ§ament geogrĂ fic. Obriu la finestra ``Establiu "
"l'emplaĂ§ament geogrĂ fic`` seleccionant l'element de menĂº ``ConfiguraciĂ³`` â†’ "
"``EmplaĂ§ament geogrĂ ficâ€¦``, prement la icona de la barra d'eines o prement "
"**Ctrl**\\ +\\ **G**."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:42
msgid ""
"Set your local time and date. You can change to any time or date by "
"selecting ``Time`` â†’ ``Set Time...`` menu item, or by pressing the ``Time`` "
"icon in the toolbar. The ``Set Time`` window uses a standard KDE Date Picker "
"widget. If you ever need to reset the clock back to the current time, just "
"select the ``Time`` â†’ ``Set Time to Now`` menu item."
msgstr ""
"Establiu la data i l'hora locals. Podeu canviar a qualsevol hora o data "
"seleccionant l'element de menĂº ``Temps`` â†’ ``Establix la data i l'horaâ€¦`` o "
"prement la icona ``Temps`` de la barra d'eines. La finestra ``Establix la "
"data i l'hora`` utilitza un giny Â«Selector de data estĂ ndardÂ» de KDE. Si mai "
"necessiteu restablir el rellotge en el temps actual, nomĂ©s cal que "
"seleccioneu l'element de menĂº ``Temps`` â†’ ``Establix el temps a ara``."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:49
msgid "Click on the ``Tools`` â†’ ``Devices`` â†’ ``Device Manager...`` menu item."
msgstr ""
"Cliqueu damunt de l'element de menĂº ``Eines`` â†’ ``Dispositius`` â†’ ``Gestor "
"de dispositiusâ€¦``."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:52
msgid "Under the ``Device`` column, select your telescope model."
msgstr "En la columna ``Dispositiu``, trieu el model del vostre telescopi."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:54
msgid "Click on the ``Run Service`` button."
msgstr "Cliqueu damunt del botĂ³ ``Inicia el servei``."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:56
msgid "Click ``Close`` to leave the Device Manager Dialog."
msgstr ""
"Cliqueu damunt ``Tanca`` per a eixir del diĂ leg Â«Gestor de dispositiusÂ»."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:60
msgid ""
"You do not need to set the geographic location and time every time you "
"connect to a telescope. Only adjust the settings as needed."
msgstr ""
"No vos caldrĂ  establir l'emplaĂ§ament geogrĂ fic i el temps cada vegada que "
"connecteu amb un telescopi. NomĂ©s cal ajustar les preferĂ¨ncies segons calga."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:64
msgid ""
"You are now ready to use the device features, KStars conveniently provides "
"two interchangeable GUI interfaces for controlling telescopes:"
msgstr ""
"Ara ja esteu preparat per a utilitzar les caracterĂ­stiques del dispositiu, "
"KStars proporciona dues interfĂ­cies amb IGU convenientment intercanviables "
"per al control dels telescopis:"

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:68
msgid "**Controlling your telescope**"
msgstr "**Controlar el telescopi**"

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:70
msgid ""
"``Sky map Control``: For each device you run in the ``Device Manager``, a "
"corresponding entry will show up in popup menu that allows you to control "
"the properties of the device. You can issue commands like **Slew**, "
"**Sync**, and **Track** directly from the sky map."
msgstr ""
"``Control des del mapa celeste``: per a cada dispositiu que executeu al "
"``Gestor de dispositius``, apareixerĂ  una entrada corresponent al menĂº "
"emergent que us permetrĂ  controlar les propietats del dispositiu. Podeu "
"executar ordres com ara **Orienta**, **Sincronitza** i **Seguix** "
"directament des del mapa celeste."

