#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:81
msgid ""
"``INDI Control Panel``: The panel offers the user with all the features "
"supported by a device."
msgstr ""
"``Quadro de control INDI``: el quadro oferix a l'usuari totes les "
"caracterĂ­stiques admeses per un dispositiu."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:84
msgid "The panel is divided into three main sections:"
msgstr "El quadro es dividix en tres seccions principals:"

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:86
msgid ""
"``Device tabs``: Each additional active device occupies a tab in the INDI "
"panel. Multiple devices can run simultaneously without affecting the "
"operation of other devices."
msgstr ""
"``Pestanyes de dispositiu``: cada dispositiu actiu addicional ocupa una "
"pestanya al quadro INDI. MĂºltiples dispositius poden funcionar "
"simultĂ niament sense afectar l'operaciĂ³ dels altres."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:91
msgid ""
"Property views on the ``Main Control`` and ``Options`` tabs: Properties are "
"the key element in INDI architecture. Each device defines a set of "
"properties to communicate with the client. The current position of the "
"telescope is an example of a property. Semantically similar properties are "
"usually contained in logical blocks or groupings."
msgstr ""
"Vistes de propietats en les pestanyes ``Control principal`` i ``Opcions``: "
"Les propietats sĂ³n l'element clau de l'arquitectura INDI. Cada dispositiu "
"definix un conjunt de propietats per a comunicar-se amb el client. La "
"posiciĂ³ actual del telescopi Ă©s l'exemple d'una propietat. Les propietats "
"semĂ nticament similars solen estar contingudes en blocs o agrupacions "
"lĂ²giques."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:99
msgid ""
"``Log viewer``: Devices report their status and acknowledge commands by "
"sending INDI messages. Each device has its own log view. A device usually "
"sends messages to its device driver only, but a device is permitted to send "
"a generic message when appropriate."
msgstr ""
"``Visor del registre``: els dispositius informen del seu estat i reconeixen "
"les ordres enviant missatges INDI. Cada dispositiu tĂ© la seua prĂ²pia vista "
"del registre. Un dispositiu usualment nomĂ©s envia missatges al seu "
"controlador de dispositiu, perĂ² a un dispositiu se li permet enviar un "
"missatge genĂ¨ric quan siga necessari."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:106
msgid "|image3|"
msgstr "|image3|"

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:108
msgid ""
"You are not restricted on using one interface over another as they can be "
"both used simultaneously. Actions from the ``Sky map`` are automatically "
"reflected in the ``INDI Control Panel`` and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"No teniu cap restricciĂ³ a l'hora d'utilitzar una interfĂ­cie per damunt d'una "
"altra, ja que es poden utilitzar ambdues simultĂ niament. Les accions des del "
"``Mapa celeste`` es reflectixen automĂ ticament al ``Quadro de control INDI`` "
"i viceversa."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:113
msgid ""
"To connect to your telescope, you can either select ``Connect`` from your "
"device popup menu or alternatively, you can press ``Connect`` under your "
"device tab in the INDI ``Control Panel``."
msgstr ""
"Per a connectar-vos amb el telescopi, podeu seleccionar ``Connecta`` des del "
"menĂº emergent del dispositiu o, de manera alternativa, podeu prĂ©mer "
"``Connecta`` davall la pestanya del dispositiu al ``Quadro de control INDI``."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:119
msgid ""
"By default, KStars will try to connect to the ``/dev/ttyS0`` port. To change "
"the connection port, select the ``Tools`` â†’ ``Devices`` â†’ ``INDI Control "
"Panel...`` menu item and change the port under your device tab."
msgstr ""
"De manera predeterminada, KStars intentarĂ  connectar-se amb el port ``/dev/"
"ttyS0``. Per a canviar el port de connexiĂ³, trieu l'element de menĂº "
"``Eines`` â†’ ``Dispositius`` â†’ ``Quadro de control INDIâ€¦`` i canvieu el port "
"en la pestanya del dispositiu."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:124
msgid ""
"KStars automatically updates the telescope's longitude, latitude, and time "
"based on current settings in KStars. You can enable/disable these using the "
"``INDI`` page from the ``Settings`` â†’ ``Configure KStars...`` menu item. "
"Using the ``INDI`` page you can configure KStars to display or not INDI "
"status messages in the status bar. By default INDI server port numbers have "
"values between the range from 7624 to 9000, but you can easily change the "
"range using the ``From:`` and ``To:`` text boxes from the ``Server Port`` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"KStars actualitza automĂ ticament la longitud, la latitud i el temps del "
"telescopi segons la configuraciĂ³ actual de KStars. Podeu des/activar-les "
"mitjanĂ§ant la pĂ gina ``INDI`` des de l'element de menĂº ``ConfiguraciĂ³`` â†’ "
"``Configura KStarsâ€¦``. MitjanĂ§ant la pĂ gina ``INDI`` podeu configurar KStars "
"per a mostrar o no els missatges d'estat INDI en la barra d'estat. De manera "
"predeterminada, els nĂºmeros de port del servidor INDI tenen valors entre "
"7624 i 9000, perĂ² podeu canviar amb facilitat l'interval mitjanĂ§ant els "
"quadros de text ``De:`` i ``A:`` de la secciĂ³ ``Port del servidor``."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:134
msgid ""
"If KStars communicates successfully with the telescope, it will retrieve the "
"current RA and DEC from the telescope and will display a crosshair on the "
"sky map indicating the telescope position. You can hide the crosshair that "
"marks telescope position using ``INDI`` page from the ``Settings`` â†’ "
"``Configure KStars...`` menu item."
msgstr ""
"Si KStars es comunica correctament amb el telescopi, recuperarĂ  l'AR i la "
"Dec actuals des del telescopi i mostrarĂ  una creu en el mapa celeste que "
"indicarĂ  la posiciĂ³ del telescopi. Podeu ocultar la creu que marca la "
"posiciĂ³ del telescopi mitjanĂ§ant la pĂ gina ``INDI`` des de l'element de menĂº "
"``ConfiguraciĂ³`` â†’ ``Configura KStarsâ€¦``."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:144
msgid "**Synchronizing your telescope**"
msgstr "**Sincronitzar el telescopi**"

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:146
msgid ""
"If you aligned your telescope and the last alignment star was, for example, "
"Vega, then the crosshair should be centered around Vega. If the crosshair "
"was off target, then you can right-click Vega from the sky map and select "
"**Sync** from your telescope menu. This action will instruct the telescope "
"to synchronize its internal coordinates to match those of Vega, and the "
"telescope's crosshair should now be centered around Vega."
msgstr ""
"Si heu alineat el telescopi i l'Ăºltima estrela d'alineaciĂ³ ha sigut, per "
"exemple, Vega, el punt de mira hauria d'estar centrat al voltant de Vega. Si "
"el punt de mira estava fora de l'objectiu, podeu fer clic dret damunt Vega "
"des del mapa celeste i triar **Sincronitza** des del menĂº del telescopi. "
"Esta acciĂ³ indicarĂ  al telescopi que sincronitze les seues coordenades "
"internes perquĂ¨ coincidisquen amb les de Vega, i el punt de mira del "
"telescopi ara hauria d'estar centrat al voltant de Vega."

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:155
msgid "This is it: your telescope is ready to explore the heavens!"
msgstr "AĂ§Ă² Ă©s tot: el vostre telescopi estĂ  llest per a explorar el cel!"

#: ../../user_manual/indi-telescope-setup.rst:159
msgid ""
"Never use the telescope to look at the sun. Looking at the sun might cause "
"irreversible damage to your eyes and your equipment."
msgstr ""
"No utilitzeu mai el telescopi per a mirar al Sol. Mirar-lo podria causar "
"danys irreversibles als vostres ulls, aixĂ­ com al vostre equip."

